# Topaz Docker / registry

- **Portainer / GitHub deploy (recommended):** pull `ghcr.io/carshyne/topaz:latest` via `docker-compose.portainer.yml`
- **GitHub repo:** `https://github.com/CarShyne/Topaz` — compose path must be `docker-compose.portainer.yml` (not `docker-compose.yml` with build)
- **Docker Hub mirror (optional):** `jt7777/topaz:latest` — only after pushing to Hub manually or via Actions secrets
- Do **not** use `jt7777/topaz` or `carshyne/topaz` in Portainer unless that image actually exists on the registry

GitHub Actions builds `ghcr.io/carshyne/topaz:latest` on every push to `main`.
